projected benefit obligations for pension by $385 million, the year-end 2005
u.s. accumulated benefit obligations for pension by $349 million and the 2005
u.s. accumulated postretirement benefit
obligation by $93
million. this change also increased pension expenses for 2006 by
$64million and postretirement expenses by $17 million.
